Necessary:
Create Tag: Ground, Tower, Wall, Build
Create Layer(important sequenz): (8)PostProcessing,(9)Player,(10)Tower,(11)Build

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PLAYER:

On player: placeAndUI, Capsule Collider with slide Material

Cam: MainCamera

Tower: Size 1-9 : Tower Prefab 

Texture: Size 1-9 : Tower Texture

Image: Ignore if filled else : in to scene : UI Prefab : fill Image RawImage 0-8

True Material: Material (Green)

False Material: Material (Red)

Place Range: value max place Range of tower

Layer: accept : Default,TransparentFX,Ignore Raycast,PostProcessing,Tower
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
set Tag : Player

set Layer : Player
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TOWER(Prefab):

On Tower: towerPlaceScript, BoxCollider : enable : isTrigger

Layer:  accept : Default,TransparentFX,Ignore Raycast,PostProcessing,Water,Player,Tower
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
set Tag : Tower

set Layer : Tower
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Remarks:

Wall Gameobjects : Tag : Wall (if dont know this)
Ground Gameobjects : Tag : Ground (only this tower place able)
Water Gameobjects: Tag : Water
